latestPosts.caption:
A bride who’d give you the chunni off her back - literally! 💕

Avantika’s bridesmaids have been her rock, but if you ask them, they’ll tell you she’s the kindest soul, always putting them before herself. Case in point: one’s wearing her chunni, the other her heels🥹✨

Catch this beautiful bond in Nykaa Wali Shaadi Episode 4, now streaming on @officialjiocinema.

#Nykaa #NykaaWaliShaadi

P.S. Avantika’s phera outfit by @taruntahiliani, topped off with a custom couture veil, is an absolute showstopper!

latestPosts.caption:
Introducing our fabulous cover stars for this festive edition: @sanagrover, @elladverma, @kompalmattakapoor, and @avantikkkaaaa, bringing their stunning patakha glam to life! 

As we transition from August to the New Year, the whirlwind of festivals and wedding celebrations makes it feel like we’re constantly changing clothes, indulging in sweets, and planning the next big event. This festive season is all about the madness, the joy of reconnecting with family and friends (even virtually), and keeping up with trends while embracing the spirit of celebration.

This edition is a heartfelt curation that resonates with everyone’s festive spirit, featuring style guides for fashion and decor while reminding readers to plan their budgets wisely for get-togethers and gifting.

With diyas, lights, flowers, and all things festive warming our hearts, we hope these stories inspire you as much as they inspire us. Here’s to a joyous festive season! Are you ready to celebrate?
